sequenceDiagram
    participant H as Human
    participant S as Forge Skills
    participant A as Artifacts
    participant AI as AI Agent
    participant E as External

    rect rgb(235, 240, 255)
        Note over H,E: COMPANY SETUP (one-time per install)
        H->>S: /company-add [name] (or --quick for defaults)
        S-->>H: 7-topic grilling — cadence, team locations, holidays, freeze periods, compliance, approval gate, AI policy
        S->>A: ~/.claude/companies/[name]/config.md
        Note over S,A: /company-git to connect team remote · /company-sync to stay current
    end

    rect rgb(240, 240, 255)
        Note over H,E: IDEATION
        H->>S: pitch idea
        S->>A: IDEA-NNN assigned + idea.md + diagram.mmd + estimate
        S-->>H: ACCEPT / DECLINE / HOLD
        H->>S: accept → /create-project
        S->>AI: scaffold + commit (PROJ-NNN assigned)
        AI->>E: push to git remote
        Note over S,A: registry.md updated — IDEA-NNN → PROJ-NNN cross-ref
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over H,E: PLANNING
        H->>S: /grill-with-docs (planning phase entry point)
        S-->>H: Q+A loop — checks CONTEXT.md + codebase + ADRs
        S->>A: CONTEXT.md updated inline (Avoid aliases, Flagged Ambiguities)
        S->>A: research/*.md (optional) · /prototype (optional)
        H->>S: confirm scope → /write-prd
        S->>AI: Phase 1 — AFK explore
        AI-->>S: scope summary + per-module estimates
        H->>S: confirm → Phase 2 write
        S->>A: prd/active/*.md (with estimates + Estimate Status)
        H->>S: /testplan → TC-NNN assigned per test case
        S->>A: testplan-*.md + docs/tests/registry.md updated
        S->>A: /estimate → story points + token bands confirmed
        S->>A: /break-down → kanban.md tickets (with S|M|L|XL | Npts tags)
        Note over H,S: /grill-me for ad-hoc stress-testing only
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 240)
        Note over H,E: SPRINT MANAGEMENT
        H->>S: /sprint-start
        S->>AI: read company config — sprint_length_weeks + freeze period + public holiday check
        S->>AI: capacity check vs preferences.md (story pts + token budget)
        AI-->>H: ⚠️ over capacity / XL ticket warnings / ❄️ freeze overlap / 🗓️ holiday flags
        S->>A: sprint-NN.md (with Public Holidays & Freeze Periods field)
        loop Every session
            AI->>S: /standup — reads company config for upcoming freeze + team holiday flags
            S-->>H: daily brief + token spend + deadline flags + ❄️ freeze warnings
        end
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 200)
        Note over H,E: BUILD
        H->>S: /build — type CONFIRM
        S->>AI: read company config — ai_human_signoff_required + ai_data_restrictions
        S->>AI: buffer window check · pre-build health check (.claude/deploy.md)
        loop AFK ticket loop
            S->>AI: execute ticket (with CODING-STANDARDS + TESTING loaded)
            AI->>AI: red → green → refactor (/tdd)
            AI->>AI: lightweight PII scan per ticket
            AI->>A: kanban.md (real time) + actual token band recorded
            Note over AI,A: context checkpoint every 3 tickets if 3+ remain
            alt ai_human_signoff_required: true
                S-->>H: ✋ AI policy — type APPROVED to mark ticket Done
            end
        end
        S-->>H: ⏸ HITL pause — type CONTINUE
        AI-->>S: 2× failure → /diagnose
        S->>A: docs/tokens/[feature].md — build phase recorded
        S->>A: docs/metrics/metrics-log.md — diagnose events logged
        S-->>H: build summary
    end

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over H,E: QA
        S->>A: /qa-plan → qa-plan.md (TC-NNN IDs carried from testplan)
        S-->>H: human works through checklist (tick TC-NNN items)
        S->>AI: /pii-check Phase 1 — AFK scan (codebase + docs)
        Note over S,AI: reads ai_data_restrictions from company config — surfaced in report header
        AI->>A: pii-report.md (AI policy + Necessary / Incidental findings)
        S-->>H: /pii-check Phase 2 — HITL review one finding at a time
        S->>A: docs/tokens/[feature].md — QA phase recorded
        H->>S: type APPROVE → /approve
        S->>A: PRD archived + HANDOFF reset + token ledger updated
        S-->>H: 💡 consider /pir [PROJ-NNN] — did this feature achieve its stated goals?
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 245)
        Note over H,E: SPRINT CLOSE
        S->>AI: /sprint-end Phase 1 — AFK draft
        AI->>A: sprint-NN.md + HANDOFF (Session type: Sprint Close)
        AI->>A: docs/metrics/metrics-log.md — sprint velocity row appended
        S-->>H: /sprint-end Phase 2 — HITL retro
        H->>S: confirm
        S->>A: kanban-archive.md (estimated vs actual bands)
        S->>A: ~/.claude/companies/[name]/retrospectives/sprint-NN-retro.md
        Note over S,A: Sprint token total surfaced
    end

    rect rgb(245, 240, 255)
        Note over H,E: PI MANAGEMENT — Go/No Go Gate
        S->>AI: /go-nogo — reads company config (freeze periods, compliance tier, external approval gate, release_cadence/release_day)
        AI->>A: gono-brief.md (freeze check + external approval section if configured)
        S-->>H: GO / NO-GO decision
        Note over H,S: NO-GO → /sprint-replan or /diagnose suggested
        H->>S: /changelog — generate release notes from kanban + DEVLOG + git log
        S->>A: CHANGELOG.md + user-facing release summary
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 240)
        Note over H,E: DEPLOY
        H->>S: /deploy — type CONFIRM
        S->>AI: Go/No Go gate check + company deployment_chain cross-check vs .claude/deploy.md
        Note over S,AI: deployment_manual_gates add HITL pauses before each gated environment
        AI->>E: staging deploy
        AI-->>H: health check ✓ — type PROMOTE
        H->>S: PROMOTE confirmed
        AI->>E: production deploy
        AI->>A: deploy-log.md + diagram-v5-deployed
        S-->>H: 💡 consider /pir [PROJ-NNN] — did it achieve its goals in production?
        Note over H,E: On failure: ROLLBACK / INVESTIGATE / STOP — never auto-rollback

        H->>S: /deploy-pi (full PI in sequence by deploy-order)
        S->>AI: deploy project 1 → 2 → N
        AI->>A: PI plan per-project status (✅ Deployed / ❌ Failed / ⏳ Pending)

        H->>S: /rollback or /rollback-pi (emergency — no Go/No Go gate)
        S-->>H: present last good version + require reason
        AI->>E: rollback (reverse deploy-order for /rollback-pi)
        S-->>H: DIAGNOSE handoff on success
    end

    rect rgb(245, 240, 255)
        Note over H,E: PI CLOSE
        H->>S: /pi-end
        S->>A: PI plan archived + stakeholder delivery summary
        Note over S,A: PI token total from ledger surfaced
        S->>E: stakeholder delivery summary
        H->>S: /pir PI-N — PI-level review across all delivered features
        S-->>H: HITL outcome assessment — did features achieve stated goals?
        S->>A: ~/.claude/companies/[name]/pir/PI-N/pir-YYYY-MM-DD.md
        Note over S,A: PIR gaps feed /fy-review as primary data source
    end

    Note over H,E: SESSION MANAGEMENT — available at any stage
    Note over H,S: /continue (resume from HANDOFF.md) · /handoff (any planned pause — writes HANDOFF.md) · /debrief (end-of-day — also updates kanban + DEVLOG) · /save-state (emergency)
    Note over H,S: /standup (daily orient) · /scope-check · /backlog-add · /backlog-list · /backlog-proj · /lookup

    Note over H,E: CODE QUALITY & SECURITY — available at any stage
    Note over H,S: /critic · /review · /write-adr · /security-assessment · /security-resolve · /performance-review · /dependency-update
    Note over H,S: /lang-rules · /push-standards · /accessibility · /ai-first-engineering · /diagnose · /write-article

    Note over H,E: KNOWLEDGE BASE — available at any stage
    Note over S,A: /knowledge-onboard · /add-system · /add-project · /ingest · /publish · /setup-confluence
    Note over S,A: /knowledge-health · /context-health · /add-term · /update-context · /summarise-system · /style-check

    Note over H,E: METRICS & REPORTING — available at any stage
    Note over S,A: /token-report · /dashboard-tokens · /context-health · /fy-review · /pir

    Note over H,E: MAINTENANCE — available at any stage
    Note over S,A: /feature-flag · /tech-debt · /dependency-update · /incident · /standalone-release · /sprint-replan · /pi-replan · /link-jira

    Note over H,E: FRAMEWORK — available at any stage
    Note over S,A: /write-a-skill · /learn · /evolve · /assimilate · /commands · /onboard · /create-project

    Note over H,E: TOKEN RECORDING — AFK automatic at end of each phase
    Note over A,AI: docs/tokens/[feature].md updated per phase → ~/.claude/tokens/ledger.md at /approve

    Note over H,E: ID SYSTEM — assigned automatically, never reused
    Note over A,AI: IDEA-NNN · PROJ-NNN · TC-NNN · SEC-YYYYMMDD-NNN · PERF-YYYYMMDD-NNN · INC-NNN → /lookup resolves any ID
